| `poc_app/src/api_endpoints.py` | HTTP endpoint handler functions |
| `poc_app/maps/endpoint.json` | HTTP endpoint definitions (8 endpoints) |
| `poc_app/docker-compose.yml` | Kafka, Redis, Jaeger, Kafka-UI, Postgres |

