## Known Limitations

- **1 worker per input topic** ŌĆö enforced by design (deterministic routing, safe backpressure)
- **`KAFKA_BULK_OUTPUT_SYNC=True` + high `max_workers`** ŌĆö each bulk job waits synchronously for broker ACKs via a shared producer; with 100 concurrent threads this creates contention; set `KAFKA_BULK_OUTPUT_SYNC=False` or reduce `max_workers` for bulk workers
- **`commit_strategy="before"`** ŌĆö at-most-once; messages may be lost on crash after commit but before processing
